! --- Hardware Verification ---
Switch# show running-config
! Verified 24 FastEthernet ports and 2 Gigabit ports
! Verified 16 Virtual Terminal (VTY) lines (0-15) 

! --- NVRAM Check ---
Switch# show startup-config
! Result: "startup-config is not present" 
! Reason: No configuration has been saved to NVRAM yet.

! --- Initial Basic Configuration ---
S1(config)# hostname S1                       ! Assign unique device name

! --- Line & Access Security ---
S1(config)# line console 0                    ! Access physical console port
S1(config-line)# password letmein             ! Set plain-text console password
S1(config-line)# login                        ! Enable password prompt at login
S1(config-line)# exit

! --- Privilege Level Security ---
S1(config)# enable password c1$c0             ! Set weak enable password
S1(config)# enable secret itsasecret          ! Set strong MD5 encrypted password

! --- Global Hardening & Banners ---
S1(config)# service password-encryption       ! Encrypt all plain-text passwords
S1(config)# banner motd #Authorized Access Only!# ! Legal notice for login screen

! --- Final Save ---
S1# copy running-config startup-config        ! Save RAM to NVRAM to prevent data loss
